description:
AKI makes everything easier!

Simple as going to ATM / Internet Banking or our agents to load your account and start using all the services of Vouchers/Recharges and Payments existing in the platform.

Available Services: Movicel, Net One and ZAP Satellite, GH Kids, Balance Transfer
Soon: DSTv, Angola Telecom, ENDE, EPAL, and other surprises ...

Agents:
We have commissions for agents.
Contact us via email or phone (Monday to Friday from 9am to 5pm).

How it works:
- Download the application;
- Query your code / reference in Balance screen in the Queries menu of the application;
- Then go to a Multicaixa/ATM or Internet Banking, go to the option of Payment by Reference, and you use your Entity and Balance Reference that you saw in Balance screen in the application;
- After all the steps in Multicaixa or Internet Banking, the value you recharge will appear in AKI in less than 1 minute;
- Once the balance appears in the Application you can use it to purchase any existing product or service in the application.
